@heath 
I have green light to proceed with go-live on the farm fresh page for DSA. Can you please let me know the process given DSA currently has a staging URL in place?

Logged 10mins to Harvest

@chris please check

Hi @ricaV2 done following updates

✅ Can we please reduce the size of the icons? Think they’re slightly too large at the moment.
✅ Could we update the copy for Enjoyable Jobs to: Creating sustainable jobs that are rewarding and meaningful.
✅ Can we see how the header will look if the Farm Fresh logo is larger?

https://dsa-staging.wolfiq.cloud/farm-fresh-v1

Time: +10mins

action.text: Rica Rosario Valencia assigned to Jaime Velasquez

full_threads.body:
Hi Rika,

Please see below for further updates to the Farm Fresh page Jaime assisted with earlier today.

Please tag me once complete!

Hi Chris,

Happy Monday! Hope you had a good weekend 😊

Can we please reduce the size of the icons? Think they’re slightly too large at the moment.


Could we update the copy for Enjoyable Jobs to:
Creating sustainable jobs that are rewarding and meaningful.

Can we see how the header will look if the Farm Fresh logo is larger? Think it’s getting lost because of the size.

Thank you! Almost there woohoo!
Brittany Tudela​​
